Octopilot MCP Server
Copyright 2024 Octopilot (https://octopilot.app)

This product includes software developed by Octopilot.

The Octopilot MCP server implements the Model Context Protocol (MCP)
to expose Octopilot's pipeline toolchain to AI agents. It enables
agents to detect project languages, generate CI/CD configuration, and
onboard repositories to the Octopilot pipeline in a single call.

If you use or redistribute this software, this NOTICE file must be
included in full in any distribution, documentation, or derived work
(Apache License 2.0, Section 4(d)).

For installation and documentation, visit:
  https://mcp.octopilot.app

Source code:
  https://github.com/octopilot/octopilot-mcp
